// =============================================================================
// FUTURE DATA MODELS — OYO-Like Expansion Architecture
// =============================================================================
//
// STATUS: REFERENCE ONLY — NOT USED BY PRISMA
// These models define the target data architecture for Phase 2, Phase 3,
// and National Scale phases. They are NOT part of the active schema.
//
// USAGE:
//   When starting a new phase, move relevant models into schema.prisma,
//   run `npx prisma migrate dev --name phase_X_feature_name`, and update
//   the service layer.
//
// RELATIONSHIP TO CURRENT SCHEMA:
//   - Extends existing: Hotel, User, Inquiry, PartnerApplication
//   - New domains: Booking, Payment, Commission, Review, Franchise, Pricing
//   - Geography (Country/Region/City) already supports multi-city
//
// =============================================================================


// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// PHASE 2A: PARTNER STANDARDIZATION & SCORING
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// Upgrade: Link User (HOTEL_PARTNER) → Hotel, add quality scoring

// New enum — extends existing UserRole with future roles
